          <li><a href="/">プロフィール</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <button class="header-search">🔍</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- フルwidth スライダー -->
  <div class="slider-section">
    <div style="position:relative;">
      <div class="slider-track" id="sliderTrack">
        <div class="slide" onclick="location.href='/posts/soelu-review/'">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&h=480&q=80" alt="">
          <div class="slide-overlay"><span class="slide-cat">ヨガ体験談</span><div class="slide-title">【体が硬い・体調不安な私でも】SOELUオンラインヨガを試した正直な体験談</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506126613408-eca07ce68773?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&h=480&q=80" alt="">
          <div class="slide-overlay"><span class="slide-cat">ウェルネス習慣</span><div class="slide-title">おうち時間を整える、40〜50代のウェルネス習慣</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599901860904-17e6ed7083a0?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&h=480&q=80" alt="">
          <div class="slide-overlay"><span class="slide-cat">初心者ガイド</span><div class="slide-title">ヨガマット1枚から始める、おうちウェルネスのはじめかた</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510894347713-fc3dc6166ef5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&h=480&q=80" alt="">
          <div class="slide-overlay"><span class="slide-cat">ヨガ体験談</span><div class="slide-title">朝5分でできる、体が硬い人のための目覚めストレッチ</div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <img class="slide-img" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552196563-55cd4e45efb3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&h=480&q=80" alt="">
          <div class="slide-overlay"><span class="slide-cat">ウェルネス習慣</span><div class="slide-title">疲れを翌日に持ち越さない、夜のリラックスルーティン</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="slider-btn prev" onclick="changeSlide(-1)">‹</button>
      <button class="slider-btn next" onclick="changeSlide(1)">›</button>
    </div>
    <div class="slider-nav">
      <button class="dot active" onclick="goSlide(0)"></button>
      <button class="dot" onclick="goSlide(1)"></button>
      <button class="dot" onclick="goSlide(2)"></button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- スライダー下：2カラム -->
  <div class="site-body">
    <main class="main-content">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </main>

    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">PROFILE</div>
        <div class="profile-avatar">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=180&h=180&q=80" alt="ひかる">
        </div>
        <div class="profile-name">ひかる</div>
        <div class="profile-sub">おうちウェルネス管理人</div>
        <p class="profile-text">おうちヨガを通じて、毎日を少しずつ整えています。40〜50代の方へ、正直な体験談をお届けします。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">POPULAR</div>
        <ul class="popular-list">
          <li class="popular-item">
            <span class="popular-num">1</span>
            <img class="popular-thumb" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=128&h=92&q=80" alt="">
            <a href="/posts/soelu-review/" class="popular-title">【体が硬い・体調不安な私でも】SOELUオンラインヨガを試した正直な体験談</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">CATEGORY</div>
        <ul class="cat-list">
          <li><a href="/"><span>ヨガ体験談</span><span class="cat-count">1</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>ウェルネス習慣</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>初心者ガイド</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>アイテム紹介</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">TAGS</div>
        <div class="tag-cloud">
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">SOELU</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">オンラインヨガ</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">初心者</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">体が硬い</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">40代</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">リラックス</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">おうち時間</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">ウェルネス</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-logo">おうちウェルネス</div>
    <p class="footer-desc">体が硬くても、体調不安でも。おうちからはじめるウェルネスライフ</p>
    <nav class="footer-nav">
      <a href="/">ホーム</a><a href="/">プロフィール</a>
      <a href="/">プライバシーポリシー</a><a href="/">お問い合わせ</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 おうちウェルネス</p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    let current = 0;
    const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.slide');
    const total = slides.length;
    const track = document.getElementById('sliderTrack');
    function goSlide(n) {
      const vis = window.innerWidth <= 768 ? 1 : 3;
      const max = total - vis;
      current = Math.max(0, Math.min(n, max));
      track.style.transform = `translateX(-${current * slides[0].offsetWidth}px)`;
      document.querySelectorAll('.dot').forEach((d,i) => d.classList.toggle('active', i === current));
    }
    function changeSlide(dir) { goSlide(current + dir); }
    setInterval(() => {
      const vis = window.innerWidth <= 768 ? 1 : 3;
      goSlide(current >= total - vis ? 0 : current + 1);
    }, 4000);
    let sx = 0;
    track.addEventListener('touchstart', e => sx = e.touches[0].clientX);
    track.addEventListener('touchend', e => { const d = sx - e.changedTouches[0].clientX; if(Math.abs(d)>40) changeSlide(d>0?1:-1); });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
